reviews.text: Shopping mall similar to those in most new housing estates.  Same JHC, Pizza Hut, Manning, Aeon, etc.  No surprises.  You definitely will be shocked by the dirtiest toilets in this shopping mall though.
Its a local residential shopping center. It’s nice and  decent parking for the car.
very nice. I enjoyed walking around the mall.

Quite disorganized, but has a large variety of products on sale, from fashion, food to trending gadgets. Washrooms available on request but are not the cleanest in the area. Very close to a metro station and easy access to a large assortment of bus routes to almost all destinations possible.
Not the best place to be in if you expect high-end treatment, but a great place if you want to spend some money on fashion and food.

Very unique shopping center filled with everything from food to fashion to toys and gadgets..It was a lucky surprise to walk in and find a great toy store just before a birthday party. Post office is inside too
